<span class="smalltext">“There is no doubt that Mr. Künstler today is America’s foremost painter of historic and heroic paintings.”<br />
        <em>- The late Lemon Saks, owner, Saks Galleries, Denver, Co.</em><br />
       </span><br />
        <table width="1%" align="center">
