<span class="smalltext">“I knew how I felt about the exhibition. I wanted to know how Mr. Künstler felt about the overwhelming response, the crowds, the hoopla. ‘It’s been so gratifying, I’ve finally had an exhibition in my own home town,’ said the artist who has had shows all over the world. ‘And this is about my paintings. It’s not just Civil War buffs.”<br />
        <em>- Arlene Epstein South Shore Record</em><br />
       </span><br />
        <table width="1%" align="center">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="smalltext"></td>
