<span class="smalltext">“Künstler is a superb historian as well as a truly gifted painter. That explains why he has gained a nation’s respect.”<br />
        <em>- James I. Robertson, Jr. Author, Stonewall Jackson</em><br />
       </span><br />
        <table width="1%" align="center">
